        "subject": "LU-2827 tests: add version check to recovery-small test 113",
        "message": "LU-2827 tests: add version check to recovery-small test 113\n\nThis patch adds Lustre version check codes into recovery-small\ntest 113 to make the test interoperate with servers that do not\nhave the following changes:\n\nLustre-commit: b1cbd2a87580e26afa07a799a897ce9881980439\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/5978\nor\nLustre-commit: 1984882771ba22f36b5d3d61f94b98268abaf4ca\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/10492\n\nTest-Parameters: alwaysuploadlogs envdefinitions=ONLY=113 \\\nossjob=lustre-b2_5 mdsjob=lustre-b2_5 ossbuildno=86 mdsbuildno=86 \\\ntestlist=recovery-small\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9b6ebb0ed100af120ecd1d70e1c37ebe1c6b36b8\n"
